videos.headline: Johnson spins and breaks free for long run
videos.description: Jaguars RB Xavier Johnson turns a short run into a huge gain by spinning out of a tackle and running for 47-yards before getting tripped up downfield.

videos.headline: Garvin finds Way for tying score
videos.description: South Alabama QB Cole Garvin throws it up for grabs  and WR Jamarius Way comes down with the 29-yard TD reception.

videos.headline: Veal turns on the jets for catch-and-run TD
videos.description: Louisiana Tech's J'Mar Smith connected with WR Teddy Veal who turns an out rout up-field and outruns the South Alabama defense for the tying score.

videos.headline: Smith rolls right and throws TD dart
videos.description: Louisiana State QB J'Mar Smith fakes a power run out of a three-back formation and finds an open Jarred Craft in the back corner of the end zone for touchdown.

videos.headline: Cooper intercepts Garvin overthrow
videos.description: Suoth Alabama's Cooper Garvin overthrows an open Jaguars receiver and the errant pass is intercepted by Louisiana Tech's Secdrick Cooper.

videos.headline: Cooper makes great read on second pick
videos.description: South Alabama RB Xavier Johnson looks open for a touchdown, but Secdrick Cooper jumps the rout and intercepts Cole Gervin on the goal line to protect the Bulldogs' 17-7 lead.

videos.headline: Garvin-to-Harris connection sets up field goal
videos.description: South Alabama WR Sam Harris shakes his defender and catches a 27-yard pass from Cole Garvin to set up a field goal near the end of the first half.

videos.headline: Scott finds hole and scores long TD
videos.description: Louisiana Tech extends their fourth quarter lead as Boston Scott jump cuts into space and scores a 27-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Coach Holtz looks forward to conference play after resilient win
videos.description: Louisiana Tech's Skip Holtz credits solid defense and big plays in the fourth quarter for the win as his team looks forward to UAB next week.
